cdata.name: Ar.cash
cdata.desc:
Ar.cash is a distributed and uncensorable archivefor the internetbased on an new blockchain-like data structure, the blockweave.Through a distributed consensus system, the information associated with an internet URL can be sotedon Ar.cash's blockweave, linkeing it cryptographically with every other block (and document) on the Ar.cash, makingcontent on the internet to be made immutable.

Ar.cash's mining system maints the security properties of the SHA2-256 Proof of Work system, while theProof of Access algorithm solves the problem of blockchain scalability by creating a self-organising data storage network. ARC tokens are used to interact with the Ar.cash network.
